1
00:01:14,200 --> 00:01:15,480
You two,

2
00:01:15,800 --> 00:01:17,440
and you, go with him.

3
00:01:17,440 --> 00:01:17,920
Okay.

4
00:01:19,280 --> 00:01:20,280
Run faster.

5
00:01:26,200 --> 00:01:27,640
Mingshu, what's going on?

6
00:01:27,640 --> 00:01:28,680
It's done. Now,

7
00:01:28,840 --> 00:01:29,560
when I shout,

8
00:01:29,560 --> 00:01:31,520
you guys immediately sneak onto the ship.

9
00:01:31,520 --> 00:01:32,050
Mingshu,

10
00:01:32,280 --> 00:01:32,960
where are you going?

11
00:01:32,960 --> 00:01:33,840
These two brothers and I...

12
00:01:33,840 --> 00:01:35,039
I'll go distract Yamada.

13
00:01:35,039 --> 00:01:36,240
Otherwise, you won't be able to board the ship.

14
00:01:36,240 --> 00:01:36,800
No.

15
00:01:37,800 --> 00:01:38,800
It's too dangerous.

16
00:01:38,800 --> 00:01:39,400
Yeah, bro.

17
00:01:39,560 --> 00:01:40,080
If you go out now,

18
00:01:40,080 --> 00:01:41,360
won't you be a sitting duck?

19
00:01:41,360 --> 00:01:42,890
Don't worry. We'll split up

20
00:01:43,080 --> 00:01:43,920
to make sure you get on the ship.

21
00:01:43,920 --> 00:01:44,280
No.

22
00:01:44,440 --> 00:01:45,680
We can't let you risk yourself again.

23
00:01:45,680 --> 00:01:46,479
You can't go.

24
00:01:48,360 --> 00:01:48,960
Trust me.

25
00:01:49,440 --> 00:01:50,320
I will definitely be on the ship

26
00:01:50,320 --> 00:01:51,380
to meet up with you.

27
00:01:51,759 --> 00:01:52,360
Bro.

28
00:01:52,880 --> 00:01:53,479
Say no more.

29
00:01:53,479 --> 00:01:54,400
It's now or never.

30
00:01:54,400 --> 00:01:54,930
Jiadong,

31
00:01:55,000 --> 00:01:55,800
come with me.

32
00:02:01,000 --> 00:02:01,530
Jiadong.

33
00:02:02,040 --> 00:02:02,600
These are the Qiaopi

34
00:02:02,600 --> 00:02:04,080
entrusted to me by the organization.

35
00:02:04,080 --> 00:02:05,480
If anything happens to me,

36
00:02:05,480 --> 00:02:06,760
please make sure to take them out.

37
00:02:06,760 --> 00:02:07,720
No, Mingshu.

38
00:02:08,160 --> 00:02:09,360
I'll go distract Hashan and his men.

39
00:02:09,360 --> 00:02:10,039
You have a mission to complete.

40
00:02:10,039 --> 00:02:10,800
You can't take this risk.

41
00:02:10,800 --> 00:02:11,320
No.

42
00:02:11,760 --> 00:02:12,640
I have more experience dealing with them

43
00:02:12,640 --> 00:02:13,440
than you do.

44
00:02:14,400 --> 00:02:15,000
Jiadong.

45
00:02:16,079 --> 00:02:18,280
Take good care of Dad and Wangshu for me.

46
00:02:18,520 --> 00:02:19,320
See you later.

47
00:02:19,440 --> 00:02:20,440
Brother Mingshu.

48
00:02:25,840 --> 00:02:27,040
Chen Jiadong is here!

49
00:02:27,120 --> 00:02:27,920
Go after him!

50
00:02:29,240 --> 00:02:30,440
Come with me quickly.

51
00:02:38,200 --> 00:02:39,440
Don't let Brother Mingshu's efforts be in vain.

52
00:02:39,440 --> 00:02:40,120
Let's go quickly.

53
00:02:40,120 --> 00:02:40,450
Come.

54
00:02:40,640 --> 00:02:41,400
Dad, Dad, let's go quickly.

55
00:02:41,400 --> 00:02:42,640
Come here.

56
00:02:48,600 --> 00:02:49,600
Chen Jiadong is here!

57
00:02:49,600 --> 00:02:50,360
Go after him!

58
00:02:52,320 --> 00:02:52,920
Brothers,

59
00:02:53,560 --> 00:02:54,680
capture Chen Jiadong alive.

60
00:02:54,680 --> 00:02:57,010
President Yamada will reward us greatly.

61
00:02:57,400 --> 00:02:58,130
Go after him!

62
00:03:17,400 --> 00:03:18,720
Chen Jiadong,

63
00:03:19,320 --> 00:03:21,480
you have no way out.

64
00:03:23,200 --> 00:03:26,200
President Yamada said,

65
00:03:27,160 --> 00:03:30,240
if you surrender,

66
00:03:31,000 --> 00:03:33,000
you will be well fed and well treated,

67
00:03:33,000 --> 00:03:35,520
and he will find you eight wives.

68
00:03:36,600 --> 00:03:38,860
Just think about it, isn't it beautiful?

69
00:03:44,240 --> 00:03:44,880
Go!

70
00:03:47,240 --> 00:03:48,960
Did something explode over there?

71
00:03:48,960 --> 00:03:50,360
Will brother be alright?

72
00:03:52,040 --> 00:03:52,960
Oh no,

73
00:03:53,360 --> 00:03:54,400
it's a trap.

74
00:03:54,680 --> 00:03:56,760
Quick, back to the dock!

75
00:03:57,840 --> 00:03:59,300
The boat is about to leave.

76
00:03:59,640 --> 00:04:00,840
Can Mingshu make it?

77
00:04:06,480 --> 00:04:07,120
Here he comes.

78
00:04:07,120 --> 00:04:08,320
Brother Mingshu is here.

79
00:04:08,320 --> 00:04:09,920
Great, brother is fine.

80
00:04:10,880 --> 00:04:11,520
Mingshu,

81
00:04:11,720 --> 00:04:12,920
get on the boat quickly!

82
00:04:12,920 --> 00:04:14,120
Brother, hurry up!

83
00:04:14,480 --> 00:04:15,760
Stop right there!

84
00:04:16,600 --> 00:04:17,200
Chase him!

85
00:04:19,839 --> 00:04:20,370
Brother!

86
00:04:20,519 --> 00:04:21,240
Mingshu!

87
00:04:21,399 --> 00:04:22,079
Brother!

88
00:04:22,440 --> 00:04:23,080
Brother!

89
00:04:23,720 --> 00:04:25,200
Brother Mingshu, don't let go!

90
00:04:25,200 --> 00:04:26,120
Mingshu, I'll pull you up!

91
00:04:26,120 --> 00:04:26,800
Mingshu!

92
00:04:27,400 --> 00:04:28,260
I didn't expect

93
00:04:28,800 --> 00:04:31,600
that it was you who caught me this time.

94
00:04:35,800 --> 00:04:36,440
You brat!

95
00:04:36,920 --> 00:04:37,640
I got him.

96
00:04:37,880 --> 00:04:38,600
Hurry up.

97
00:04:40,920 --> 00:04:41,450
Brother,

98
00:04:41,760 --> 00:04:43,490
you caught me twelve years ago.

99
00:04:43,760 --> 00:04:44,560
Twelve years later,

100
00:04:44,560 --> 00:04:45,800
it's my turn to pull you up.

101
00:04:45,800 --> 00:04:47,000
Hold tight, brother.

102
00:04:52,400 --> 00:04:52,930
Brother,

103
00:04:53,200 --> 00:04:54,480
hold on a little longer.

104
00:04:54,480 --> 00:04:55,720
Don't scare me, okay?

105
00:04:56,800 --> 00:04:57,440
Mingshu,

106
00:04:58,560 --> 00:04:59,420
you'll be fine.

107
00:04:59,760 --> 00:05:00,400
Hold on.

108
00:05:00,680 --> 00:05:01,800
Brother, hold on.

109
00:05:02,240 --> 00:05:03,760
Doctor! Is there a doctor?

110
00:05:04,520 --> 00:05:05,450
Somebody, help!

111
00:05:06,160 --> 00:05:06,760
Brother.

112
00:05:07,600 --> 00:05:08,280
Dad.

113
00:05:10,480 --> 00:05:11,010
Jiadong.

114
00:05:12,320 --> 00:05:13,080
Wangshu.

115
00:05:15,400 --> 00:05:16,860
I don't think I'll make it.

116
00:05:19,480 --> 00:05:20,120
Dad,

117
00:05:21,960 --> 00:05:22,680
I'm sorry.

118
00:05:24,360 --> 00:05:27,000
I've made you worry for all these years.

119
00:05:28,480 --> 00:05:29,560
Don't be silly.

120
00:05:30,560 --> 00:05:31,240
All these years,

121
00:05:31,240 --> 00:05:32,840
you've always been my pride.

122
00:05:35,360 --> 00:05:36,159
Jiadong,

123
00:05:37,960 --> 00:05:39,760
take good care of Wangshu for me.

124
00:05:40,640 --> 00:05:42,040
No, brother.

125
00:05:43,360 --> 00:05:44,920
I can't replace you.

126
00:05:45,040 --> 00:05:46,720
Brother, don't go.

127
00:05:46,880 --> 00:05:48,810
I can't live without you, brother.

128
00:05:49,120 --> 00:05:49,760
Brother,

129
00:05:50,240 --> 00:05:51,480
hold on a little longer.

130
00:05:51,480 --> 00:05:52,760
Let me bandage you properly,

131
00:05:52,760 --> 00:05:53,920
okay, brother?

132
00:05:54,600 --> 00:05:55,240
Jiadong,

133
00:05:57,240 --> 00:05:57,920
remember.

134
00:05:58,880 --> 00:06:00,740
The remittance letter I gave you,

135
00:06:02,600 --> 00:06:03,160
you must,

136
00:06:03,600 --> 00:06:05,240
you must send it back to

137
00:06:07,200 --> 00:06:08,930
Shuncheng Remittance Bureau.

138
00:06:09,640 --> 00:06:10,320
Okay.

139
00:06:13,880 --> 00:06:14,600
Brother.

140
00:06:14,640 --> 00:06:15,400
Mingshu.

141
00:06:15,880 --> 00:06:17,880
Brother Mingshu! Brother Mingshu!

142
00:06:17,960 --> 00:06:18,840
Brother.

143
00:06:19,240 --> 00:06:20,240
Brother Mingshu.

144
00:06:20,240 --> 00:06:20,960
Brother Mingshu.

145
00:06:20,960 --> 00:06:21,760
Brother.

146
00:06:26,520 --> 00:06:27,600
Brother.

147
00:06:28,520 --> 00:06:30,280
Brother,

148
00:06:31,960 --> 00:06:34,440
please don't leave me, okay?

149
00:06:35,960 --> 00:06:37,560
Mingshu.

150
00:06:45,120 --> 00:06:46,120
Brother Mingshu.

151
00:06:46,440 --> 00:06:48,040
You saved my life back then.

152
00:06:48,600 --> 00:06:49,560
We once escaped death together

153
00:06:49,560 --> 00:06:50,960
in these mountains.

154
00:06:52,040 --> 00:06:53,360
But now you're gone.

155
00:06:54,200 --> 00:06:55,600
I will definitely avenge

156
00:06:55,720 --> 00:06:57,120
your death.

157
00:07:16,920 --> 00:07:18,440
Malayan Chinese businesses

158
00:07:18,440 --> 00:07:20,100
called upon patriotic groups

159
00:07:20,120 --> 00:07:21,640
and overseas Chinese merchants

160
00:07:21,640 --> 00:07:23,600
to jointly raise 3,000 silver dollars.

161
00:07:23,600 --> 00:07:25,640
Please have the Quanzhou Shuncheng Remittance Office receive it

162
00:07:25,640 --> 00:07:27,800
and forward it to the Pingtan Guerrilla Detachment

163
00:07:27,800 --> 00:07:29,460
to purchase necessary grain,

164
00:07:29,640 --> 00:07:30,240
clothing,

165
00:07:30,560 --> 00:07:32,159
and weapons and ammunition.

166
00:07:37,600 --> 00:07:38,600
Brother Mingshu.

167
00:07:38,800 --> 00:07:40,159
I will also complete

168
00:07:40,720 --> 00:07:42,180
your unfinished mission.

169
00:07:45,200 --> 00:07:45,680
Hello.

170
00:07:46,120 --> 00:07:48,480
I'm here to deliver the remittance letter from Malaya.

171
00:07:48,480 --> 00:07:49,320
Why is it you?

172
00:07:50,080 --> 00:07:51,080
Where is Mingshu?

173
00:08:04,560 --> 00:08:05,120
Jiadong,

174
00:08:06,360 --> 00:08:07,960
thank you for your hard work.

175
00:08:09,280 --> 00:08:11,840
I didn't expect Mingshu's trip to Malaya

176
00:08:13,000 --> 00:08:14,330
would cost him his life.

177
00:08:16,480 --> 00:08:17,320
Oh, Mingshu.

178
00:08:17,880 --> 00:08:18,880
The mission you completed

179
00:08:18,880 --> 00:08:19,940
was done very well.

180
00:08:22,480 --> 00:08:23,640
Liang, I'm sorry.

181
00:08:24,600 --> 00:08:25,800
Mingshu was killed

182
00:08:25,880 --> 00:08:26,600
to save us.

183
00:08:27,480 --> 00:08:29,140
I will definitely avenge him.

184
00:08:29,600 --> 00:08:30,800
It's not just for him.

185
00:08:32,280 --> 00:08:33,400
We must also avenge

186
00:08:33,799 --> 00:08:35,240
the millions of compatriots killed

187
00:08:35,240 --> 00:08:36,169
by the Japanese.

188
00:08:37,320 --> 00:08:38,000
But...

189
00:08:39,320 --> 00:08:40,200
I currently have

190
00:08:40,200 --> 00:08:41,659
an urgent mission on hand.

191
00:08:42,400 --> 00:08:44,059
Someone needs to go to Malaya.

192
00:08:44,440 --> 00:08:46,170
It was originally for Mingshu.

193
00:08:46,400 --> 00:08:47,280
To Malaya?

194
00:08:47,840 --> 00:08:48,800
What is the mission?

195
00:08:48,800 --> 00:08:50,200
Can I complete it for him?

196
00:08:53,040 --> 00:08:54,680
This mission is urgent.

197
00:08:55,680 --> 00:08:56,240
We need someone

198
00:08:56,240 --> 00:08:57,680
to secretly deliver this remittance letter

199
00:08:57,680 --> 00:08:59,000
in the shortest time possible

200
00:08:59,000 --> 00:08:59,930
to the President

201
00:09:00,080 --> 00:09:01,600
of the Malayan Chinese Chamber of Commerce,

202
00:09:01,600 --> 00:09:02,600
Qin Muyang.

203
00:09:03,280 --> 00:09:04,800
But you just came back from Malaya.

204
00:09:04,800 --> 00:09:05,560
I can go.

205
00:09:06,440 --> 00:09:07,440
What Mingshu was going to do

206
00:09:07,440 --> 00:09:08,040
must be

207
00:09:08,080 --> 00:09:09,320
of great significance.

208
00:09:09,320 --> 00:09:10,040
I can complete

209
00:09:10,040 --> 00:09:11,170
his mission for him.

210
00:09:13,120 --> 00:09:14,250
Thank you, Jiadong.

211
00:09:16,000 --> 00:09:17,840
You must deliver it safely.

212
00:09:18,360 --> 00:09:18,840
Okay.

213
00:09:19,120 --> 00:09:19,920
Rest assured.

214
00:09:21,040 --> 00:09:21,680
What?

215
00:09:22,200 --> 00:09:23,400
We just got back.

216
00:09:23,840 --> 00:09:25,300
Why are you leaving again?

217
00:09:25,680 --> 00:09:26,960
Stop messing around.

218
00:09:28,080 --> 00:09:30,280
Mingshu just died there.

219
00:09:31,320 --> 00:09:32,720
You know how dangerous

220
00:09:32,760 --> 00:09:33,880
Malaya is.

221
00:09:34,080 --> 00:09:35,680
How can you go back now?

222
00:09:36,240 --> 00:09:37,160
Yes, Jiadong.

223
00:09:37,720 --> 00:09:39,580
Don't scare your sister-in-law.

224
00:09:49,840 --> 00:09:50,570
What's this?

225
00:09:59,240 --> 00:10:00,240
Jiadong, this...

226
00:10:03,160 --> 00:10:03,720
Jiadong,

227
00:10:04,240 --> 00:10:05,520
is this true?

228
00:10:06,720 --> 00:10:07,440
It's true.

229
00:10:08,120 --> 00:10:08,760
So I must

230
00:10:08,800 --> 00:10:10,240
return to Malaya immediately.

231
00:10:10,240 --> 00:10:11,200
To tell Mr. Qin and the others

232
00:10:11,200 --> 00:10:12,120
this news.

233
00:10:12,800 --> 00:10:13,840
This matter

234
00:10:14,920 --> 00:10:16,320
is of course very urgent.

235
00:10:17,400 --> 00:10:18,480
But why does it have to be

236
00:10:18,480 --> 00:10:19,600
you who delivers it?

237
00:10:19,600 --> 00:10:20,520
You are a

238
00:10:20,520 --> 00:10:21,520
sitting duck now.

239
00:10:22,800 --> 00:10:24,160
Can't someone else go?

240
00:10:24,920 --> 00:10:26,160
It's too dangerous.

241
00:10:27,160 --> 00:10:28,400
I asked to go myself.

242
00:10:28,960 --> 00:10:29,640
Why?

243
00:10:29,680 --> 00:10:30,400
Nonsense.

244
00:10:31,960 --> 00:10:32,640
Jiadong,

245
00:10:33,200 --> 00:10:33,840
you are

246
00:10:33,920 --> 00:10:34,920
a married man now.

247
00:10:35,440 --> 00:10:37,200
You can't be so willful.

248
00:10:37,880 --> 00:10:38,560
Dad.

249
00:10:39,280 --> 00:10:41,140
This was Mingshu's last mission.

250
00:10:41,400 --> 00:10:42,760
He sacrificed himself for us.
